---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import PremiumBadge from '../components/PremiumBadge';
---

<Layout
  title="Quality Ingredients in Premium Cat Litter"
  description="Learn about the natural, safe ingredients that make premium cat litter superior. From activated charcoal to natural clays, understand what goes into quality litter."
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <PremiumBadge client:load variant="gold">Ingredient Transparency</PremiumBadge>
      <h1>What Makes Premium<br /><span class="gradient-text">Ingredients Matter</span></h1>
      <p class="page-hero__subtitle">
        The secret to superior performance lies in carefully selected, natural ingredients
        that work together to create the ultimate litter experience.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Key Ingredients -->
  <section class="ingredients section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="ingredients-grid">
        <div class="ingredient-card ingredient-card--featured">
          <div class="ingredient-card__badge">
            <PremiumBadge client:load variant="dark" size="sm">Star Ingredient</PremiumBadge>
          </div>
          <div class="ingredient-card__icon">&#9899;</div>
          <h3>Activated Charcoal / Biochar</h3>
          <p class="ingredient-card__intro">
            The gold standard in natural odor elimination.
          </p>
          <div class="ingredient-card__details">
            <h4>How It Works</h4>
            <p>
              Activated charcoal has an incredibly porous surface structure—a single gram
              contains over 3,000 square meters of surface area. This allows it to trap
              and hold odor molecules at the molecular level, rather than masking them.
            </p>
            <h4>Benefits</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>Eliminates ammonia and sulfur compounds</li>
              <li>100% natural and non-toxic</li>
              <li>Sustainable when sourced from wood waste</li>
              <li>Continues working for weeks</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <a
            href="https://purrify.ca/learn/science?utm_source=premiumcatlitter&utm_medium=ingredients"
            class="btn btn-primary"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
          >
            Learn About Purrify's Formula
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="ingredient-card">
          <div class="ingredient-card__icon">&#127960;</div>
          <h3>Natural Bentonite Clay</h3>
          <p class="ingredient-card__intro">
            Premium-grade clay for instant, solid clumping.
          </p>
          <div class="ingredient-card__details">
            <h4>How It Works</h4>
            <p>
              Bentonite clay absorbs moisture and expands, forming tight clumps around
              waste. Premium grades are carefully processed to maximize clumping speed
              and minimize dust.
            </p>
            <h4>Benefits</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>Instant clump formation</li>
              <li>Easy scoop-out without crumbling</li>
              <li>Naturally antibacterial</li>
              <li>Highly absorbent</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="ingredient-card">
          <div class="ingredient-card__icon">&#129717;</div>
          <h3>Natural Zeolites</h3>
          <p class="ingredient-card__intro">
            Volcanic minerals that neutralize ammonia.
          </p>
          <div class="ingredient-card__details">
            <h4>How It Works</h4>
            <p>
              Zeolites have a unique honeycomb structure that traps ammonia molecules
              through an ion-exchange process, effectively removing the primary source
              of litter box odor.
            </p>
            <h4>Benefits</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>Specifically targets ammonia</li>
              <li>Naturally occurring mineral</li>
              <li>Extends litter life</li>
              <li>Non-toxic if ingested</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="ingredient-card">
          <div class="ingredient-card__icon">&#127795;</div>
          <h3>Plant-Based Fibers</h3>
          <p class="ingredient-card__intro">
            Sustainable materials from wood, corn, or wheat.
          </p>
          <div class="ingredient-card__details">
            <h4>How It Works</h4>
            <p>
              Natural fibers provide structure, absorption, and a soft texture. Premium
              formulas use sustainably sourced fibers processed to be dust-free and
              highly absorbent.
            </p>
            <h4>Benefits</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>Biodegradable and compostable</li>
              <li>Lightweight and easy to handle</li>
              <li>Soft on sensitive paws</li>
              <li>Pleasant natural scent</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What to Avoid -->
  <section class="avoid section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header text-center">
        <h2>Ingredients to Avoid</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle">
          Not all litter ingredients are created equal. Watch out for these
          potentially problematic components.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="avoid-grid">
        <div class="avoid-card">
          <div class="avoid-card__icon">&#9888;</div>
          <h4>Artificial Fragrances</h4>
          <p>
            Strong perfumes can irritate sensitive cats and mask rather than
            eliminate odors. Many cats avoid heavily scented litters.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="avoid-card">
          <div class="avoid-card__icon">&#9888;</div>
          <h4>Sodium Bentonite (Low Grade)</h4>
          <p>
            Cheap sodium bentonite can swell in the digestive tract if ingested,
            causing blockages. Premium calcium bentonite is safer.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="avoid-card">
          <div class="avoid-card__icon">&#9888;</div>
          <h4>Silica Dust</h4>
          <p>
            Fine crystalline silica particles can cause respiratory issues with
            prolonged exposure for both cats and humans.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="avoid-card">
          <div class="avoid-card__icon">&#9888;</div>
          <h4>Chemical Clumping Agents</h4>
          <p>
            Synthetic polymers and chemicals used to enhance clumping may not
            be safe if groomed off paws and ingested.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Reading Labels -->
  <section class="labels section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content-grid">
        <div class="content-main">
          <h2>How to Read Litter Labels</h2>
          <p>
            Understanding ingredient labels helps you make informed decisions. Here's
            what to look for when shopping for premium litter.
          </p>

          <h3>Look For</h3>
          <ul class="check-list">
            <li>"99% dust-free" or "virtually dust-free"</li>
            <li>"Natural ingredients" or "plant-based"</li>
            <li>"Activated charcoal" or "biochar"</li>
            <li>"No artificial fragrances"</li>
            <li>"Veterinarian recommended"</li>
            <li>Clear ingredient listing</li>
          </ul>

          <h3>Watch For</h3>
          <ul class="cross-list">
            <li>"Fresh scent" without specifying source</li>
            <li>Vague ingredient descriptions</li>
            <li>No dust claims at all</li>
            <li>"Odor control" without explaining how</li>
            <li>Very long ingredient lists</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <aside class="content-sidebar">
          <div class="info-card">
            <h4>Quality Certifications</h4>
            <p>Look for these marks of quality:</p>
            <ul class="cert-list">
              <li>
                <span class="cert-list__icon">&#9989;</span>
                <span>Veterinarian Recommended</span>
              </li>
              <li>
                <span class="cert-list__icon">&#127807;</span>
                <span>Eco-Certified</span>
              </li>
              <li>
                <span class="cert-list__icon">&#128062;</span>
                <span>Pet Safe</span>
              </li>
              <li>
                <span class="cert-list__icon">&#127968;</span>
                <span>Made in USA/Canada</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </aside>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Premium Ingredients, Premium Results</h2>
      <p>
        Purrify combines activated biochar with natural clays for unmatched
        odor control and clumping performance.
      </p>
      <div class="cta-buttons">
        <a
          href="https://purrify.ca/products?utm_source=premiumcatlitter&utm_medium=ingredients"
          class="btn btn-primary btn-lg"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
        >
          Shop Purrify
        </a>
        <a
          href="https://purrify.ca/learn/science?utm_source=premiumcatlitter&utm_medium=ingredients"
          class="btn btn-secondary btn-lg"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
        >
          Our Science
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style lang="scss">
  @use '../styles/variables' as *;
  @use '../styles/mixins' as *;

  .page-hero {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, $color-cream 0%, $color-champagne 100%);
    padding: $spacing-16 0 $spacing-20;
    text-align: center;

    h1 {
      margin-top: $spacing-6;
      margin-bottom: $spacing-6;
    }

    &__subtitle {
      font-size: $font-size-lg;
      color: $color-text-secondary;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
  }

  .ingredients {
    background: $color-white;
  }

  .ingredients-grid {
    display: grid;
    gap: $spacing-6;

    @include md {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  .ingredient-card {
    background: $color-cream;
    border-radius: $border-radius-lg;
    padding: $spacing-8;
    position: relative;

    &--featured {
      background: $color-charcoal;
      color: $color-cream;

      @include md {
        grid-column: span 2;
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: auto 1fr;
        gap: $spacing-8;
      }

      h3 {
        color: $color-gold;
      }

      h4 {
        color: $color-gold-light;
      }

      p {
        color: rgba($color-cream, 0.8);
      }

      .ingredient-card__details {
        @include md {
          grid-column: 2;
          grid-row: 1 / span 4;
        }
      }
    }

    &__badge {
      margin-bottom: $spacing-4;
    }

    &__icon {
      font-size: 48px;
      margin-bottom: $spacing-4;
    }

    h3 {
      font-size: $font-size-xl;
      margin-bottom: $spacing-3;
    }

    &__intro {
      font-size: $font-size-md;
      margin-bottom: $spacing-6;
    }

    &__details {
      h4 {
        font-family: $font-body;
        font-size: $font-size-sm;
        font-weight: $font-weight-semibold;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.05em;
        margin-bottom: $spacing-3;
        margin-top: $spacing-5;

        &:first-child {
          margin-top: 0;
        }
      }

      p {
        font-size: $font-size-sm;
        margin-bottom: $spacing-3;
      }

      ul {
        font-size: $font-size-sm;

        li {
          padding-left: $spacing-5;
          position: relative;
          margin-bottom: $spacing-2;

          &::before {
            content: '✓';
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            color: $color-gold;
          }
        }
      }
    }

    .btn {
      margin-top: $spacing-6;
    }
  }

  .avoid {
    background: $color-ivory;
  }

  .section-header {
    margin-bottom: $spacing-12;

    h2 {
      margin-bottom: $spacing-4;
    }
  }

  .section-subtitle {
    font-size: $font-size-lg;
    color: $color-text-secondary;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .avoid-grid {
    display: grid;
    gap: $spacing-6;

    @include sm {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }

    @include lg {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    }
  }

  .avoid-card {
    background: $color-white;
    border-radius: $border-radius-lg;
    padding: $spacing-6;
    border-left: 4px solid #E57373;

    &__icon {
      font-size: 24px;
      margin-bottom: $spacing-3;
    }

    h4 {
      font-size: $font-size-md;
      margin-bottom: $spacing-3;
    }

    p {
      font-size: $font-size-sm;
      color: $color-text-secondary;
      margin: 0;
    }
  }

  .labels {
    background: $color-cream;
  }

  .content-grid {
    display: grid;
    gap: $spacing-12;

    @include lg {
      grid-template-columns: 1.5fr 1fr;
      gap: $spacing-16;
    }
  }

  .content-main {
    h2 {
      margin-bottom: $spacing-4;
    }

    h3 {
      margin-top: $spacing-8;
      margin-bottom: $spacing-4;
      font-size: $font-size-lg;
      color: $color-gold-dark;
    }

    > p {
      font-size: $font-size-md;
    }
  }

  .check-list, .cross-list {
    li {
      padding-left: $spacing-6;
      position: relative;
      margin-bottom: $spacing-3;
      font-size: $font-size-md;

      &::before {
        position: absolute;
        left: 0;
        font-size: $font-size-base;
      }
    }
  }

  .check-list li::before {
    content: '✓';
    color: $color-gold;
  }

  .cross-list li::before {
    content: '✗';
    color: #E57373;
  }

  .content-sidebar {
    @include lg {
      position: sticky;
      top: 100px;
      height: fit-content;
    }
  }

  .info-card {
    background: $color-white;
    border-radius: $border-radius-lg;
    padding: $spacing-6;
    box-shadow: $shadow-md;

    h4 {
      font-size: $font-size-lg;
      margin-bottom: $spacing-3;
    }

    > p {
      font-size: $font-size-sm;
      color: $color-text-secondary;
      margin-bottom: $spacing-4;
    }
  }

  .cert-list {
    li {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: $spacing-3;
      padding: $spacing-3 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba($color-charcoal, 0.1);
      font-size: $font-size-sm;

      &:last-child {
        border-bottom: none;
      }
    }

    &__icon {
      font-size: $font-size-lg;
    }
  }

  .cta-section {
    background: $color-charcoal;
    padding: $spacing-16 0;
    text-align: center;

    h2 {
      color: $color-cream;
      margin-bottom: $spacing-4;
    }

    p {
      color: rgba($color-cream, 0.8);
      font-size: $font-size-lg;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto $spacing-8;
    }
  }

  .cta-buttons {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: $spacing-4;
    justify-content: center;
  }
</style>
